(1237, 162, 'accordions_content_title', 'a:9:{i:0;s:34:\"<em>frank</em>Â Lounge â $15,000\";i:1535916277438;s:33:\"Content Block Sponsor â $15,000\";i:1535916278137;s:46:\"TheÂ <em>frank</em>Â Puzzle Hunt â $15,000Â \";i:1535916279315;s:41:\"Tuesday Night Welcome Rally â $12,000Â \";i:1535916506280;s:51:\"Wednesday Connectorâs Lunch Sponsor â $10,000Â \";i:1535916527319;s:36:\"Thursday Lunch Sponsor â $10,000Â \";i:1535916527986;s:38:\"<em>frank</em> After Party â $10,000\";i:1535916528629;s:36:\"The DailyÂ <em>frank</em> âÂ $5000\";i:1535916529376;s:40:\"<em>frank</em>Â Lounge Snacks â $5,000\";}'),
(1238, 162, 'accordions_content_body', 'a:9:{i:0;s:949:\"TheÂ <em>frank</em>Â lounge provides an informal space where our attendees can connect with others and where speakers hold office hours. Each year, theÂ <em>frank</em>Â lounge reflects our theme and is filled with prompts that help our participants think about how the theme might influence their work. Located in the basement of the Hippodrome Theatre, the lounge provides a comfortable space forÂ <em>franksters</em>Â to connect in between Main Stage performances, grab a coffee or a snack, or make a quick phone call. All the Main Stage talks are live streamed onto the loungeâs four monitors.\r\nFor your support:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Signage display to acknowledge support of the lounge</li>\r\n 	<li>Name listed on materials and displays as conference sponsor atÂ <em>frank</em></li>\r\n 	<li>Logo (linked) featured prominently on Sponsors page on conference website</li>\r\n 	<li>Recognition of support onÂ <em>frankÂ </em>social media channels</li>\r\n</ul>\";i:1535916277438;s:749:\"The frank gathering features only plenary sessions which are grouped by a content theme. We schedule speakers to align their talks with the theme of each content block. In 2018, there will be seven blocks and we will work with you to identify the theme that best fits your foundationâs mission.\r\n\r\nFor your support:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Acknowledgment of sponsorship during the live stream and on the archived video recording</li>\r\n 	<li>Name listed on the program directly under the title of the content block</li>\r\n 	<li>Name listed on materials and displays as conference sponsor at frank</li>\r\n 	<li>Logo (linked) featured prominently on Sponsors page on conference website</li>\r\n 	<li>Recognition of support on frank social media channels</li>\r\n</ul>\";i:1535916278137;s:930:\"Inspired by the Washington Post Hunt, this event takes place on Thursday night and a ticket to play will be included in every franksterâs registration. People from the Gainesville community will be able to register to join the hunt as well. Designed around the theme of <em>play</em>, participants will be given two hours to search the downtown area for clues to help them solve the puzzles. The evening will end with a reveal of the winners, an award ceremony and a celebration at a venue downtown.\r\n\r\nFor your support:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Recognition of sponsorship on the hunt registration page</li>\r\n 	<li>Acknowledgment of sponsorship at the final meet up location</li>\r\n 	<li>Name listed on materials and displays as conference sponsor atÂ <em>frank</em></li>\r\n 	<li>Logo (linked) featured prominently on Sponsors page on conference website</li>\r\n 	<li>Recognition of support onÂ <em>frankÂ </em>social media channels</li>\r\n</ul>\";i:1535916279315;s:836:\"Located at the Boxcar Wine and Cheese Garden, a restored train depot in downtown Gainesville, the Welcome Rally gives <em>franksters</em> a chance to meet up with old friends and connect with new ones. <em>frank</em> connectors will be on hand to spark conversations and collaborations. Drinks and hors dâoeuvres will be served. All registered <em>franksters</em> and community <em>friends of frank</em> will be in attendance.\r\n\r\nFor your support:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Signage display to acknowledge support of the reception.</li>\r\n 	<li>Name listed on materials and displays as conference sponsor atÂ <em>frank</em></li>\r\n 	<li>Logo (linked) featured prominently on Sponsors page on conference website</li>\r\n 	<li>Recognition of support onÂ <em>frankÂ </em>social media channels</li>\r\n 	<li>Our thanks printed on cocktail napkins</li>\r\n</ul>\";i:1535916506280;s:473:\"Located inside the historic Woolworth, the buffet-style lunch is served before the official Opening Ceremonies ofÂ <em>frankÂ </em>and is included with allÂ <em>frankstersâ</em>Â registration.\r\n\r\nFor your support:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Designated as official sponsor of Connectorâs Lunch, with signage displayed at the venue</li>\r\n 	<li>Logo featured on sponsors page on conference website</li>\r\n 	<li>Recognition of support ofÂ <em>frankÂ </em>social media channels</li>\r\n</ul>\";i:1535916527319;s:422:\"Provided by a local caterer and using locally sourced foods whenever possible, Thursday lunch is included with allÂ <em>frankstersâ</em>Â registration.\r\nFor your support:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Designated as official sponsor Thursday Lunch, with signage displayed at the venue</li>\r\n 	<li>Logo featured on Sponsors page on conference website</li>\r\n 	<li>Recognition of support onÂ <em>frank</em>Â social media channels</li>\r\n</ul>\";i:1535916527986;s:439:\"Whether itâs tacos and margaritas at the Wooly or franks and bubbles outside the Hipp, our after party is a time to say goodbye, reflect and celebrate.\r\n\r\nFor your support:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Designated as official sponsor of <em>frank</em> After Party, with signage displayed at the venue</li>\r\n 	<li>Logo featured on Sponsors page on conference website</li>\r\n 	<li>Recognition of support ofÂ <em>frank</em>Â social media channels</li>\r\n</ul>\";i:1535916528629;s:470:\"The DailyÂ <em>frank</em>Â is the community newspaper of theÂ <em>frank</em>Â gathering. It includes daily highlights, weather reports, and updates on local restaurant specials.\r\n\r\nFor your support:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Designated as official sponsor of the DailyÂ <em>frank</em>, with our gratitude expressed in every issue</li>\r\n 	<li>Logo featured on Sponsors page on conference website</li>\r\n 	<li>Recognition of support ofÂ <em>frank</em>Â social media channels</li>\r\n</ul>\";i:1535916529376;s:697:\"Provide nourishing snacks and coffee to allÂ <em>franksters</em>Â in theÂ <em>frank</em>Â lounge.Â  Food and coffee will be sourced locally whenever possible. The lounge is open for 3 three days, from 9 am to 5 pm and all registeredÂ <em>franksters</em>Â have unlimited access.\r\n\r\nFor your support:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Recognition of sponsorship on the hunt registration page</li>\r\n 	<li>Acknowledgment of sponsorship at the final meet up location</li>\r\n 	<li>Name listed on materials and displays as conference sponsor atÂ <em>frank</em></li>\r\n 	<li>Logo (linked) featured prominently on Sponsors page on conference website</li>\r\n 	<li>Recognition of support onÂ <em>frank</em>Â social media</li>\r\n</ul>\";}'),
