(1518, 198, 'accordions_content_title', 'a:12:{i:1536185231546;s:56:\"This is my first <em>frank</em>. What do I need to know?\";i:0;s:27:\"When do I need to be there?\";i:1536185230256;s:40:\"What is included in my registration fee?\";i:1536185230786;s:40:\"Is my registration/ticket transferrable?\";i:1536185231917;s:41:\"Can I update my registration information?\";i:1536195969783;s:25:\"What if I need to cancel?\";i:1536185231177;s:25:\"Where do I book my hotel?\";i:1536195970328;s:27:\"How can I become a sponsor?\";i:1536185232274;s:20:\"What is Changeville?\";i:1536195969161;s:31:\"What is <em>frank</em> scholar?\";i:1536195970866;s:46:\"Arriving early or staying after the gathering?\";i:1536196208004;s:53:\"Where can I contact the organizer with any questions?\";}'),
(1519, 198, 'accordions_content_body', 'a:12:{i:1536185231546;s:330:\"At <em>frank</em> youâll connect to an instant community. We will have <em>frank</em> connectors on hand to help with your gathering questions, navigate the Recess sessions, expand your network and even recommend the best place to find chicken and waffles. A Facebook group will get you started before you arrive in Gainesville.\";i:0;s:421:\"<em>frank</em> is about community. Youâll want to be here from the moment we gather until our last\r\ngoodbye. Shared experiences are amplified, creating a vulnerability that helps establish deep\r\nmeaningful connections. The gathering opens with a Welcome Rally on Tuesday, Feb.\r\n5, 2018. We end with a goodbye party Friday, Feb. 8th. Make your travel plans\r\naccordingly! Donât forget â Changeville is Feb. 7 &amp; 8.\";i:1536185230256;s:843:\"<ul>\r\n 	<li>Tuesday: Welcome Rally featuring cocktails and hors dâoeuvres, <a href=\"http://www.depotpark.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Depot Park</a> and Boxcar Wine &amp; Beer Garden</li>\r\n 	<li>Wednesday: Lunch and evening social</li>\r\n 	<li>Thursday: Lunch and evening social</li>\r\n 	<li>Friday: Farewell after-party</li>\r\n 	<li>Coffee bucks and drink tickets, valid at area coffee shops and restaurants</li>\r\n 	<li>New friends and instant community</li>\r\n 	<li>Florida in February</li>\r\n 	<li>Access to all frank sessions in the <a href=\"http://thehipp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hippodrome Theatre</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Access to all frank social events</li>\r\n 	<li>Access to all Recess (breakout) sessions: Play, Apply, Dissect and Study</li>\r\n 	<li>Access to the frank lounge</li>\r\n 	<li>Discount to Changeville</li>\r\n</ul>\";i:1536185230786;s:289:\"You have received a personal invitation to join us at <em>frank</em>. You may not transfer your ticket to\r\nsomeone else, without first letting us know. Please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:frankgathering@gmail.com?subject=frank%202019%20conference%20question\">frankgathering@gmail.com</a>.\";i:1536185231917;s:222:\"Yes! If you want to change or add any details and donât have an Eventbrite account, simply\r\nemail us at <a href=\"mailto:frankgathering@gmail.com?subject=frank%202018%20conference%20question\">frankgathering@gmail.com</a>.\";i:1536195969783;s:308:\"We hate to see you go, but if your plans change:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Until Nov. 1, 2018 - order cancellations will be processed at full price.</li>\r\n 	<li>Nov. 1- Jan 1, 2019 â 50 percent refund</li>\r\n 	<li>After Jan. 1 , 2019- No refunds processed, but we will happily hold your ticket for frank2020.</li>\r\n</ul>\";i:1536185231177;s:1747:\"The Hampton Inn Downtown continues to be the <em>frank</em> headquarters. We have a block rate at the new AC Marriott and at the Holiday Inn University. We provide shuttle service from both of those hotels.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://urldefense.proofpoint.com/v2/url?u=http-3A__hamptoninn3.hilton.com_en_hotels_florida_hampton-2Dinn-2Dand-2Dsuites-2Dgainesville-2Ddowntown-2DGNVDTHX_index.html&amp;d=DwMFaQ&amp;c=pZJPUDQ3SB9JplYbifm4nt2lEVG5pWx2KikqINpWlZM&amp;r=5O9xPE9yiYyVNWl8_HTsADecjyEk5YcdViiJYbsFu2M&amp;m=AdaJRGjiN5WDHci5E4Gb1D-mmiIqhchwXbFgnu4Jc68&amp;s=f4jMvDAQqh2tPdy0NM6sj3viGUS53h6TyPhr3OxFJF8&amp;e=\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hampton Inn &amp; Suites Downtown Gainesville</a>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Pick dates and use the code: F19</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAC Marriott: <a href=\"https://urldefense.proofpoint.com/v2/url?u=http-3A__www.marriott.com_meeting-2Devent-2Dhotels_group-2Dcorporate-2Dtravel_groupCorp.mi-3FresLinkData-3DFRANK-2520Conferene-2520-255EGNVAC-2560FRNFRNA-257CFRNFRNB-2560169.00-2560USD-2560false-25604-25602_3_19-25602_9_19-256001_06_19-26app-3Dresvlink-26stop-5Fmobi-3Dyes&amp;d=DwMCAg&amp;c=pZJPUDQ3SB9JplYbifm4nt2lEVG5pWx2KikqINpWlZM&amp;r=5O9xPE9yiYyVNWl8_HTsADecjyEk5YcdViiJYbsFu2M&amp;m=105YirZQs0rCD6NKzMO7f7kXhTXuHZX9njQo-kup1w0&amp;s=AwN9fur6c1W3KaxontUuL6YNUWgLf2ihRr8FCbMn8Xg&amp;e=\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your group rate for FRANK Conference</a>\r\n\r\nHoliday Inn University: <a href=\"https://www.holidayinn.com/redirect?path=hd&amp;brandCode=HI&amp;localeCode=en&amp;regionCode=1&amp;hotelCode=GNVUC&amp;_PMID=99801505&amp;GPC=FNK&amp;viewfullsite=true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your group rate for FRANK Conference</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>THERE WILL BE NO SHUTTLE SERVICE FROM THE HILTON UNIVERSITY.</strong>\";i:1536195970328;s:993:\"We are hugely grateful to our supporters. They provide critical support that makes it possible to offer our participants a more affordable registration fee as well as supporting the work of the <em>frank</em> online community.\r\n\r\n<strong>OurÂ  past partners include:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Robert Wood Johnson Foundation</li>\r\n 	<li>The Joy McCann Founation</li>\r\n 	<li>Atlantic Philanthropies</li>\r\n 	<li>Al and Nancy Burnett Charitable Foundation</li>\r\n 	<li>Sarasota Community Foundation</li>\r\n 	<li>The Karel Endowment for Public Interest Communications</li>\r\n 	<li>Neimand Collaborative</li>\r\n 	<li>UF College of Journalism and Communications</li>\r\n 	<li>Visit Gainesville</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe need more people and organizations like them to keep this work going. Learn more about <a href=\"https://allisoncandreva.com/test/sponsor/\">sponsorship opportunities</a>. Contact us at <a href=\"mailto:frankgathering@gmail.com?subject=frank%202018%20conference%20question\">frankgathering@gmail.com</a>.\";i:1536185232274;s:333:\"With the mission of cultivating connections between artists, influencers and activists, <a href=\"http://changeville.us/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Changeville</a> is a festival that showcases and connects those who use music, comedy, film, virtual reality and storytelling as a vehicle to drive self-awareness and social change.\";i:1536195969161;s:285:\"frankscholar is an academic conference designed to cultivate research that will inform your practice and ignite lasting behavioral, institutional and social change. This year, frank scholar will be woven into the fabric of the frank gathering and take place during the recess sessions.\";i:1536195970866;s:161:\"Check out all the things Gainesville and Alachua County offer at <a href=\"http://www.visitgainesville.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Visit Gainesville</a>!\";i:1536196208004;s:70:\"<a href=\"mailto:frankgathering@gmail.com\">frankgathering@gmail.com</a>\";}'),
