(3203, 410, 'event_first_tab_content', '<h2>February 5-8, 2019 | Gainesville, Florida</h2>\r\n<strong>Come explore with us atÂ <i>frankÂ </i>2019. Â Between the contours of our lives, youâll find places to connect, participate and belong</strong>.\r\n\r\nThis yearÂ <em>frank</em>Â looks into the heart of social impact. Space. Reimagining space. Letting it be. Creating it. Bringing others in. Closing the space between us. The struggle with space and the tension of who and what fills it unifies the work of all who create social impact. It drives science, justice, expression and well-being. And it animatesÂ <em>frank</em>Â as a center for changing the way change is made. Space is not the final frontier. Space is the eternal canvas on which we paint and repaint progress. Join us. Weâve saved space for you.\r\n\r\n<strong><i>Registration is open and youâll get our best rates before September 15, 2018.</i></strong>'),
